g.text: Average age and row count for
1. on each one of the 4 groups defined by sex and income values, calculate total number of rows and average age
2. on each one of the 4 groups defined by sex and income values, calculate the average of all numerical columns
a. rows with missing values in column occupation
b. all rows in column occupation
c. rows with no missing value in column occupation
d. all rows in another column (i.e. marital-status). Notice that this number should be the same as the number in 2.
4. Write results from item 1. to a CSV file.
(notice that this should be the same
